I know people wonder, "So what's the use of

00:42:07.040 --> 00:42:11.780
a small project like CHABHA when the need
is so huge?"

00:42:11.780 --> 00:42:18.330
CHABHA supports the projects that work with
somewhat less than 3,000 people.

00:42:18.330 --> 00:42:23.540
It's a drop in the budget of nearly 15 million
children.

